data.description:
This delightful property situated on a corner lot with 2 Bedroom, 1 bathroom with a bonus study room currently utilized as a third bedroom. 
Inside, you'll find a cozy and well-maintained living space. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a functional layout for preparing delicious meals. Adjacent to the kitchen is a comfortable dining area, ideal for enjoying family dinners or hosting intimate gatherings. The two bedrooms has a peaceful retreat, providing plenty of natural light and sufficient closet space. The bathroom is tastefully designed and includes essential fixtures. The standout feature of this property is the versatile study room, currently being utilized as a third bedroom. This additional space can be easily transformed into a home office, playroom, or hobby area, extending flexibility to suit your needs. Step outside, and you'll discover a lovely privacy-fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation, entertaining guests, or letting your furry friends roam freely. The corner lot provides an extra sense of privacy and adds to the overall appeal of the property. Schedule a viewing and experience the inviting ambiance for yourself.
